How much time can you give me?

500
00:37:29.916 --> 00:37:31.250
You get 48 hours.

501
00:37:38.500 --> 00:37:41.250
- Yes. talk to me.
<i>- The fingerprint on the TV screen.</i>

502
00:37:41.333 --> 00:37:44.625
It's not in our database.
but we found a match.

503
00:37:44.708 --> 00:37:46.416
<i>Camilla Loen's neighbor?</i>

504
00:37:46.500 --> 00:37:48.041
No. it's not him.

505
00:37:48.125 --> 00:37:50.666
It's matching
another print in the apartment.

506
00:37:50.750 --> 00:37:51.625
Yes.

507
00:37:52.458 --> 00:37:53.458
That was Beate Lønn.

508
00:37:53.541 --> 00:37:56.166
We have a big. fat fingerprint
from a serial killer.

509
00:38:00.916 --> 00:38:02.125
Okay. come on!

510
00:38:12.750 --> 00:38:14.666
[Swedish] <i>I'm on my way. Mother.</i>

511
00:38:16.000 --> 00:38:17.791
<i>I'm on my way back.</i>

512
00:38:19.208 --> 00:38:21.666
<i>Back to my uterus.</i>

513
00:38:21.750 --> 00:38:26.250
<i>There I'll lift the knife
and cut my way in.</i>

514
00:38:35.250 --> 00:38:39.458
<i>- I was finally able to pay rent yesterday.
- My dear. don't worry about that.</i>

515
00:38:39.541 --> 00:38:41.000
I got some help anyway.

516
00:38:41.083 --> 00:38:45.291
Yes. I've noticed that there's someone
who's been coming in and out.

517
00:38:45.375 --> 00:38:48.833
- I noticed he has a dog.
- You'll get to meet him.

518
00:38:49.708 --> 00:38:52.583
But I just need to warn you
that he's different.

519
00:38:54.291 --> 00:38:56.875
He's old-fashioned.

520
00:38:57.916 --> 00:38:59.583
He doesn't want us to...

521
00:39:00.625 --> 00:39:01.583
- Wow!
- You know.

522
00:39:01.666 --> 00:39:03.541
Yeah. that's serious.

523
00:39:05.333 --> 00:39:06.583
He gave me something.

524
00:39:16.166 --> 00:39:19.416
He said that I wasn't allowed
to open it until we were engaged.

525
00:39:20.208 --> 00:39:23.208
And then he said that this is something
that lasts forever.

526
00:39:30.208 --> 00:39:31.208
<i>The Prince.</i>

527
00:39:31.291 --> 00:39:34.250
One of the gangs is gone.
and I think we have a new member.

528
00:39:34.750 --> 00:39:35.791
<i>Good!</i>

529
00:41:00.583 --> 00:41:05.541
Subtitle translation by: Trine Friis
